{
  "stem": "15732.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SIGHS] After a few days, the English changed their policy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They disappeared completely.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The army disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The watchtower, everything disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They left us alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was behind it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very clear.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We should disobey, everybody will go then different place, and then they will have solved-- solved the problem.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Certainly that we didn't let it that way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What did you do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We immediately-- we immediately decided-- first the committee talked to the people and explained that if what we went through would go all for nothing if we will dissipate, everybody going to another place in Germany.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Going back even to Foehrenwald, what would we have achieved in all that?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we would give to the English people-- the English government just a trump card.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So again, we organized ourselves, explaining to the people not to go on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then what we decided was that we have to give out [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] identity cards.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But identity cards sound somehow not the right thing, a card that acknowledges that you have been on so that wherever people-- whatever will come, we did not know, that people should be able to show to the Jewish agency that we were on So some people had cameras, so immediately started to make photos of the people so every-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] every identity card should have the-- the photo, not the name, because I-- we didn't want to divulge names if it will come in English hands by some way.",
      "word_count": 93
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So everybody had a number, a photo, and a-- and a to whom it may concern that that person was on I still have got my card and I will show it to you later.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you stay at Poppendorf?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] In Poppendorf we stayed for a short while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All together.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
